quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  17,31,"Apni aulad ko iflas (tangdasti) ke andeshey se qatal na karo, hum unhein bhi rizq denge aur tumhein bhi. Dar haqeeqat unka qatal ek badi khata hai"
  17,32,"Zina ke qareeb na phatko, wo bahut bura fail (kaam) hai aur bada hi bura raasta"
  17,33,"Qatal-e-nafs ka irtiqab na karo jisey Allah ne haraam kiya hai magar haqq ke saath, aur jo shaks mazloomana qatal kiya gaya ho uske wali ko humne qisas (retribution) ke mutalibe ka haqq ata kiya hai. Pas chahiye ke woh qatal mein hadd se na guzre, uski madad ki jayegi"
  17,34,"Maal-e-yateem ke paas na phatko magar ahsan tareeqe se, yahan tak ke woh apne shabaab (jawani) ko pahunch jaye. Ahad ki pabandi karo, beshak ahad ke barey mein tumko jawab-dehi karni hogi"
  17,35,"Paimane (measure/scales) se do to pura bhar kar do, aur tolo to theek tarazu se tolo. Yeh accha tareeqa hai aur ba-lihaz anjaam bhi yahi behtar hai"
  17,36,"Kisi aisi cheez ke peechey na lago jiska tumhein ilm na ho , yaqeenan aankh, kaan aur dil sab hi ki baaz-purs honi hai"
  17,37,"Zameen mein akad kar na chalo, tum na zameen ko phaadh sakte ho na pahadon ki bulandi ko pahunch sakte ho"
  17,38,In umoor mein se har ek ka bura pehlu tere Rubb ke nazdeek na-pasandida hai
  17,39,Yeh woh hikmat ki baatein hain jo tere Rubb ne tujhpar wahee ki hai aur dekh! Allah ke saath koi dusra mabood na bana baith warna tu jahannum mein daal diya jayega malamat zada aur har bhalayi se mehroom hokar
  17,40,Kaisi ajeeb baat hai ke tumhare Rubb ne tumhein to beton (sons) se nawaza aur khud apne liye malaika (farishton) ko betiyan bana liya? Badi jhooti baat hai jo tumlog zubaano se nikalte ho